  "summary": "Binary columnar format with mmap-based zero-copy reads. Lineitem sorted by l_shipdate + returnflag/linestatus for effective zone map skipping on Q1/Q3/Q6 date range filters. Orders sorted by orderdate for temporal query patterns. Dictionary encoding on low-cardinality strings (flags, modes, segments: 2-25 values). Delta encoding on date columns (consecutive rows have similar dates). Zone maps per 128K-row block for predicate pushdown. Sorted indexes on foreign keys (l_orderkey, o_custkey) for efficient hash joins; hash index on c_mktsegment for Q3 filtering. No sorting for small tables (25-100K rows)."
